    title: 'Captures Event-Driven Steelwork Interest',
    text: "When you erect a steel frame on a visible site, neighbours and adjacent businesses see the crane and the frame going up. They message about their own projects — extensions, mezzanines, and structural alterations. The AI converts proximity interest into steelwork leads."
