  },
  {
    question: "Can I continue Messenger conversations myself?",
    answer: "Respond in any Messenger thread and the AI yields control permanently for that conversation. It detects your reply and withdraws. Most steel firms let the AI gather the initial scope — frame type, span, tonnage, execution class, and programme timeline — then follow up to discuss connection design, crane requirements, and commercial terms."
  },
  {
    question: "How is Messenger data from steelwork queries protected?",
